payload.sql:
SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
                     pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod
                FROM pg_attribute a LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d
                  ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
               WHERE a.attrelid = '"default_texts"'::regclass
                 AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
               ORDER BY a.attnum
payload.name: SCHEMA

payload.sql:
SELECT attr.attname
            FROM pg_attribute attr
            INNER JOIN pg_constraint cons ON attr.attrelid = cons.conrelid AND attr.attnum = any(cons.conkey)
            WHERE cons.contype = 'p'
              AND cons.conrelid = '"default_texts"'::regclass
payload.name: SCHEMA

payload.sql: SELECT  "default_texts".* FROM "default_texts" WHERE "default_texts"."page" = $1  ORDER BY "default_texts"."id" ASC LIMIT 1
payload.name: DefaultText Load
